## Summary
This documentation explains how to track revenue in Amplitude, covering revenue properties ($revenue, $price, $quantity, etc.), methods for tracking both in-app and non-in-app purchases, revenue verification for IAPs, and potential causes for discrepancies between app store reports and Amplitude data.

